stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Invocation
    Invocation: CLI invocation

    Invocation --> CheckConfirm
    CheckConfirm: --confirm present?

    state CheckConfirm <<choice>>
    CheckConfirm --> Abort: no
    CheckConfirm --> CheckAuthStmt: yes

    CheckAuthStmt: --authorization-statement<br/>present + non-empty?

    state CheckAuthStmt <<choice>>
    CheckAuthStmt --> Abort: no
    CheckAuthStmt --> CheckDMA: yes

    CheckDMA: DMA transport?

    state CheckDMA <<choice>>
    CheckDMA --> CheckDMAFlag: yes
    CheckDMA --> CheckTLS: no (non-DMA)

    CheckDMAFlag: --enable-dma + euid==0<br/>+ IOMMU probe
    state CheckDMAFlag <<choice>>
    CheckDMAFlag --> Abort: missing
    CheckDMAFlag --> CheckTLS: OK

    CheckTLS: TLS-capable transport?
    state CheckTLS <<choice>>
    CheckTLS --> CheckTrust: yes
    CheckTLS --> Proceed: no (plain SSH/DMA)

    CheckTrust: known_hosts OR tls_ca provided?
    state CheckTrust <<choice>>
    CheckTrust --> Abort: no
    CheckTrust --> Proceed: yes

    Proceed: run banner + sleep + acquire
    Proceed --> [*]

    Abort: raise AuthorizationError
    Abort --> [*]
